prompts.frontCover: A vibrant and humorous watercolor painting for a greeting card front. In a charming cartoon style, a young woman is playfully trying to blow out a single, comically oversized, magical birthday candle that is almost as tall as she is. The candle, striped in whimsical pastel colors, emits a gentle, warm glow and a continuous, swirling puff of smoke that comically evades her efforts. The woman is depicted mid-action, with her cheeks puffed out, a look of playful determination on her face. A shower of soft, multi-colored watercolor confetti and tiny, floating birthday cakes drifts down around her, adding to the festive and silly atmosphere. The entire scene is rendered in a soft, flowing watercolor style with blended colors and soft edges, creating a dreamy and lighthearted feel. The background is a clean, light wash of pastel colors. Centered in the middle of the composition, written in a beautiful, flowing, and easily readable handwritten cursive script, is the text: "Happy Birthday, Lao Lao!". Flat 2D artwork style.
